{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji45","name":"毛泽东全集第45卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji45.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给杨开智的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给杨开智的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1962年11月15日）开智同志："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"得电惊悉杨老夫人逝世，十分哀痛。望你及你的夫人节哀。寄上五百元，以为悼仪。葬仪，可以与杨开慧同志我的亲爱的夫人同穴。我们两家同是一家，是一家，不分彼此。望你节哀顺变。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敬祝大安。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九六二年十一月十五日[1]杨开智，毛泽东夫人杨开慧之兄。[2]杨老夫人，指杨开智和杨开慧的母亲向振熙。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":11,"day":15}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":293,"page_end":293},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}